<HEADLINE> Russian Foreign Debt Totals 145 Billion U.S. Dollars </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Russia's foreign debt will
reach 145 billion U.S. dollars by January 1, 1999, Deputy Finance
Minister Mikhail Kasyanov said here Friday.
</P>
<P>
Kasyanov told the Ekho Moskvy radio station that the sum
include 103 billion dollars Russia inherited from the former
Soviet Union.
</P>
<P>
