the two areas which are already hard hit by food shortage makes
the problem even more critical.
</P>
<P>
He said his bureau and the authorities of the two areas have
notified the Federal Disaster Prevention and Preparedness
Commission in Addis Ababa and the eastern branch office of the
Refugees and Returnees Affairs Administration about the matter
and are waiting for a response.
</P>
<P>
Abubaker warned that the matter bears grave consequences
unless it is checked in time. 
