<HEADLINE> Henan Develops Ports of Entry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZHENGZHOU, December 26 (Xinhua) -- The rapid development of
ports and airports in central China's Henan Province over the past
decade has greatly facilitated local access to the outside world.
</P>
<P>
