<HEADLINE> China's Industrial Growth Speeds Up in October </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 26 (Xinhua) -- China's industrial sector grew
faster in October, according to the latest figures released by the
National Bureau of Statistics.
</P>
<P>
Gross industrial output value in October increased by 13.3
percent on an annual basis to 526.68 billion yuan (63.6 billion
U.S. dollars), up from the eight percent growth in the first half
of this year.
</P>
<P>
