<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Best-Selling Industrial Products in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 26 (Xinhua) -- The latest figures from the
National Bureau of Statistics showed a number of best-selling
major industrial products in the January-September period this
year.
</P>
<P>
The product sales rate of 21 major industrial products
surpassed 100 percent during the period with their stock reducing.
</P>
<P>
The product that sold best during the period is lubricating
oil, with its product sales rate hitting 115.6 percent. Following
it are synthetic rubber, with a product sales rate of 107 percent,
and range hoods, with a product sales rate of 105 percent.
</P>
<P>
The product with the lowest product sales rate is high
precision metal cutting machine tools. Its rate stands at 81.7
percent. 
</P>
</TEXT>
